# 10. Success Metrics

| Area                          | Target     |
| ----------------------------- | ---------- |
| Manual reporting reduction    | >60%       |
| Forecast accuracy improvement | +15%       |
| Dashboard response time       | <3 seconds |
| Platform availability         | 99.9%      |
| Monthly active finance users  | >85%       |
| AI recommendation acceptance  | >80%       |
