---

# 11. Risks

| Risk              | Impact | Mitigation                                     |
| ----------------- | ------ | ---------------------------------------------- |
| Poor data quality | High   | Enterprise data governance                     |
| Scope expansion   | High   | Product backlog prioritization                 |
| User adoption     | Medium | Training and change management                 |
| Security          | High   | RBAC, encryption, audit trails                 |
| AI reliability    | High   | Human review, explainability, RAG architecture |

---

