---

# 13. Recommendation

Approval is requested to initiate the Enterprise Finance Intelligence Platform program.

The program will be delivered incrementally using Agile methodologies, with measurable business outcomes reviewed at the end of each Program Increment.

The expected result is a modern Finance Intelligence Platform that improves operational efficiency, enhances executive decision-making, and establishes AI as a core capability within the Finance function.
